snippet.title: Introvert: Consequences - Official Trailer
snippet.description:
Four high school shooting survivors move to a new city and attend a 5-day group therapy program. Discover the secrets, situations, and people that await you in this surreal universe while trying to deal with the guilt and grief caused by the disturbing unforgettable past.


Music Used:
https://soundcloud.com/syvemusic/cant-find-paradise
